Major Branches of statistics:
    1. Descriptive statistics:   description and summarization of data.
    2. Inferential statistics:    Drawing of conclusions from data.


    Data: Data are the facts and figures collected.


Data Collection: 

    Data available: Published data. e.g., data.gov.in
    Data not available: need to collect, generate data.


